<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<root>
    <description>
        <group>Book</group>
        <title>정상 작동 여부 체크용 엔드포인트들</title>
        <help>Book 서비스에 요청할 수 있는 체크용 엔드포인트들 입니다.</help>
    </description>

    <tests>
        <test>
            <title>통신 확인(SanityCheck)</title>
            <help>Book 서비스에 sanityCheck 요청을 보냅니다.</help>

            <method>GET</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>sanityCheck</resourceUrl>
            <headers></headers>
            <data></data>

            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>
        
        <test>
            <title>통신 확인시에 정상으로 반환되도록 만들기(SanityCheckSetNormal)</title>
            <help>sanityCheck 요청시에 200이 반환되도록 만듭니다.</help>

            <method>PUT</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>sanityCheck/setNormal</resourceUrl>
            <headers></headers>
            <data></data>

            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>

        <test>
            <title>통신 확인시에 비정상으로 반환되도록 만들기(SanityCheckSetError)</title>
            <help>sanityCheck 요청시에 500이 반환되도록 만듭니다.</help>

            <method>PUT</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>sanityCheck/setError</resourceUrl>
            <headers></headers>
            <data></data>

            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>


        <test>
            <title>로그 얻기(Logs)</title>
            <help>Book 서비스의 로그들을 얻어옵니다.</help>

            <method>GET</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>sanityCheck/logs</resourceUrl>
            <headers></headers>
            <data></data>

            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>

        <test>
            <title>에러 로그 얻기(ErrorLogs)</title>
            <help>Book 서비스의 로그들 중에서 에러 로그만 얻어옵니다.</help>

            <method>GET</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>sanityCheck/logs?regFilter=.*ERROR.*</resourceUrl>
            <headers></headers>
            <data></data>

            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>


        <test>
            <title>0 나누기 오류 체크(DivByZeroCheck)</title>
            <help>일부로 0으로 나눠서 에러를 일으켜서 결과를 관찰합니다.</help>

            <method>GET</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>sanityCheck/divByZeroCheck</resourceUrl>
            <headers></headers>
            <data></data>

            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>

        <test>
            <title>유저 인증 여부 확인(AuthenticationCheck)</title>
            <help>HTTP 헤더로 전달된 유저 정보를 출력합니다.</help>

            <method>GET</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>sanityCheck/authenticationCheck</resourceUrl>
            <headers>
                <header key="User-Id">1</header>
                <header key="User-Role">User</header>
            </headers>
            <data></data>

            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>


        <test>
            <title>모든 책 목록 얻기(BookAll)</title>
            <help>모든 책의 목록을 얻어옵니다.</help>

            <method>GET</method>
            <baseUrl>http://localhost:8083</baseUrl>
            <resourceUrl>books</resourceUrl>
            <headers></headers>
            <data></data>
            
            <checks>
                <check type="status">2.*</check>
            </checks>
        </test>
    </tests>
</root>